        <abstract> 
<p>Asks for specimen of <hi rend="italic">Orchis latifolia</hi> and <hi rend="italic">O. maculata</hi>. " … as some Botanists doubt whether they are distinct species it would be rather curious to show them insects distinguish them".</p> 
            <p>Found a lot of bee orchids. "All facts point clearly to self-fertilisation in this species; yet I cannot swallow the bitter pill."</p>
        </abstract>
